Class PortfolioTransferable

  • java.lang.Object
    • transferable.PortfolioTransferable

  • public class PortfolioTransferable
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a class which was created to transfer the details of portfolio to the controller. This class provides details of the portfolio such as the cost basis and total value of the portfolio.
